name: ViGee Photography Gift Certificate
description:

name: Basic editing Services
description:
This listing is for my editing services on your personal in-the-home photos.  The fee starts at $15 for 10 photos.

This service will provide basic clean editing on your photos.

Basic editing includes:  Clean complexion, smooth background, adjust color, brightness, contrast. (see before and after photos for a visual).  NO COMPOSITES NO HEAD-SWAPS

Some Details:

* There are times when photos are emailed to me and they are not capable of being a great quality photo.  I will let you know if you have any of those photos.  

* It is always best to send me MORE than the total number of photos you need edited.  I will load and pick out the best for my editing services.

* Please send your photos through Dropbox.com to me.  This allows for a clean exchange between us.  I will use Dropbox to return the photos to you.

* Your photos will be sized to approximately an 8x10.  If you plan on printing them I would not suggest printing past an 8x10 or distortion of your photo is possible.

* If you would like your photos to also be put into an online gallery for purchasing prints through my professional lab it is an extra $10 fee (see options when paying for this service).  Ordering galleries are only up for 30 days.  I use a high quality professional printer to print all of my photos.

* I will not take a black and white photo and turn it into color.

* If the photo taken is blurry, the outcome will be blurry â€“ end of story!

* I will NOT edit another photographers work unless the photographer is requesting the work or if the photographer has given you editing rights to the photo(s).  You must send me the file, email or whatever you have from that photographer that states you have editing rights to the photos.  

* Basic editing does not including removal  of objects from your photo.

* I accept photos in JPEG or RAW files

*** Due to this service and digital exchange there are NO REFUNDS on this service.  As long as I am able to edit amount of  photos you've paid for, no refunds ***
